  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个群件系统里WikiPage的事件处理流程。核心是Aggregate产生事件后，经过Event Store分发，最终由Queue Worker执行副作用。你能帮我梳理一下这个时序吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Queue Worker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以Aggregate先把事件存到Event Store，然后需要有个组件把事件转成异步任务对吧？我想到可以加一个Reactor来负责Dispatch Event，然后推送到Queue里。这样分层会不会更清晰？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Reactor这个中间层很重要。Event Store把事件发给Reactor，Reactor再Push Job到Queue。然后Queue Worker从队列里取出任务处理。最后Worker要调用外部的Side Effect，比如发通知或者更新索引。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：Aggregate到Event Store是Store Event，Event Store到Reactor是Dispatch Event，Reactor推送到Queue，Queue Worker处理完再Execute Side Effect。这样五条消息顺序没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "主流程可以，但还缺异常处理。Side Effect执行完有两种结果：成功的话Worker要Mark Job as Completed；失败的话需要Retry Job。这个分支逻辑得用alt画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下分支细节：Success分支是Side Effect返回成功给Worker，然后Worker标记Queue里的任务完成；Failure分支是返回失败，然后触发Retry。这两个都是Worker发消息回Queue对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Success",
        "Failure",
        "Retry"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Worker作为主动方去更新Queue里的任务状态。Success时Mark Job as Completed，Failure时Retry Job。这样整个事件驱动的副作用处理闭环就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。六个参与者按顺序排列：Aggregate、Event Store、Reactor、Queue、Queue Worker、Side Effect。主流程五条消息，alt包裹两个分支，分别处理成功和失败场景。你看看还有要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "alt",
        "Success",
        "Failure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
